    "display_name": "Write a Satirical Article",
    "long_instructions": "## Write a Satirical Article\r\n\r\n**Before You Start:**\r\n\r\nMake sure you have filled in the **K** and **W** columns of your KWL chart for this task.\r\n\r\n**Do:**\r\n\r\nAsk AI to write a fake news article in a satirical or silly tone (like The Onion or parody news).\r\n\r\n**Try:**\r\n\r\nGive it a real news headline and ask for a satirical version.\r\n\r\n**Check:**\r\n\r\nDoes the article feel like satire (clearly fake but with a message)? Or does it seem confusing or misleading?\r\n\r\n**After You Try It:**\r\n\r\n1. Fill in the **L** column of your KWL chart\r\n2. Press **Continue** to return to the task menu\r\n",
